      info home  http://0pointer.de/lennart/projects/libdaemon/
      info use   'http://0pointer.de/lennart/projects/libdaemon/#license'
      info news  'http://0pointer.de/lennart/projects/libdaemon/#news'
      desc 'library for writing UNIX style daemons
libdaemon is a lightweight C library that
eases the process of writing UNIX style daemons.
It contains a daemonizing fork() wrapper,
a powerful syslog() wrapper, PID file management,
and signal serialization.'
